window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A fantasy tale of war, battle, and love.&nbsp;</p> <p>Ordan is the Slayer of Saina, a fearsome warrior of Frostburn. When a portal to a brand-new world opens, Ordan is tasked to march his army through and see what this new land has to offer. As victory is nigh and hopes high, native mages conspire in the confusion. Caught between two worlds, Ordan will stop at nothing to achieve his desires and save his people, no matter the cost.</p> <p>Enter a fantasy tale where might makes right, war reigns supreme, beautiful women abound, and battle is rampant. Join Ordan in the Web of Lands.</p>"; 
